---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="Contact | YWAM Sendai"
  description="Get in touch with YWAM Sendai through Discord, LINE, Instagram, email, or the application form."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <div class="stack">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Contact YWAM Sendai</p>
          <h1 class="hero-title max-w-title">
            Find the best way to connect.
          </h1>
        </div>

        <p class="lead">
          YWAM Sendai welcomes contact from prospective students, prospective staff,
          outreach teams, guests, churches, supporters, and anyone who wants to learn
          more about the community and its mission.
        </p>

        <div class="btn-group">
          <a
            href="https://discord.gg/djmCF4DBaV"
            class="btn-primary"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Join Discord
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://lin.ee/LD2Nf4b"
            class="btn-secondary-dark"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Message on LINE
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://ig.me/m/ywamsendai"
            class="btn-secondary-dark"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Message on Instagram
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-inverse-soft mb-0">
          For questions, first contact, or help finding the right next step, you can also use Ask AI.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-dark stack-sm">
        <p class="eyebrow">Quick Guide</p>
        <h2 class="card-title">How most people connect</h2>
        <p>
          For many people, messaging platforms are the easiest way to begin.
          Email is available, but it is not the main way most people first connect.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Best Ways to Connect</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Choose the contact method that fits your situation</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Different contact methods work best for different kinds of questions and next steps.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-4">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Discord</h3>
          <p>An open community space and one of the main ways people connect with YWAM Sendai.</p>
          <a
            href="https://discord.gg/djmCF4DBaV"
            class="btn-text"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Join Discord
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">LINE</h3>
          <p>Useful for informal questions, first contact, and simple conversation.</p>
          <a
            href="https://lin.ee/LD2Nf4b"
            class="btn-text"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Open LINE
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Instagram</h3>
          <p>A simple way to send a message and begin connecting.</p>
          <a
            href="https://ig.me/m/ywamsendai"
            class="btn-text"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Message on Instagram
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Email</h3>
          <p>If you prefer email, you can contact us directly.</p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@ywamsendai.org" class="btn-text">
            hello@ywamsendai.org
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Which method should I use?</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">A simple guide for different kinds of contact</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">General questions or first contact</h3>
          <p>Discord, LINE, or Instagram are usually the easiest place to begin.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">If you prefer email</h3>
          <p>Email is available for those who would rather write directly.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">If you want to take a concrete next step</h3>
          <p>
            For student applications, staff applications, outreach team inquiries,
            and guest or visitor stay inquiries, the application form is usually the best route.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="container-narrow center" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <a href="/en/apply" class="btn-secondary">Go to Application Form</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2" style="align-items: start;">
        <div class="stack-sm">
          <p class="eyebrow">Discord</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">An ongoing space for connection</h2>
          <p class="lead">
            YWAM Sendai’s Discord server is open to external people and functions as
            an ongoing communication space for the wider community.
          </p>
          <p class="text-soft">
            It includes previous DTS graduates, current participants, people connected
            for Christian community, and communication related to future DTS, DBS, and other schools.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid stack-sm">
          <article class="card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Open community space</h3>
            <p>A place where people can begin connecting and stay in touch over time.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Useful for future schools</h3>
            <p>Helpful for people interested in DTS, DBS, and other upcoming opportunities.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3 class="card-title">Good for ongoing connection</h3>
            <p>Not only for one question, but for staying connected with the wider community.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">What to Expect</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Response times may vary</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Response times depend on staff availability, ministry season, travel schedules,
          holidays, and the nature of the inquiry.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Please be patient</h3>
          <p>YWAM Sendai appreciates patience, especially during busy seasons.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Messaging is often fastest</h3>
          <p>For many people, messaging platforms are the most natural and responsive first step.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Application form for concrete requests</h3>
          <p>For formal next steps, the application form is often better than a long first email.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper border-top">
    <div class="container container-narrow center stack">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Start Here</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Reach out in the way that fits best</h2>
        <p class="lead mx-auto">
          Whether you have a simple question, want to connect with the community,
          or are ready to take a more concrete next step, we would be glad to hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
        <button type="button" class="btn-primary open-hub-trigger">Ask AI</button>
        <a href="/en/apply" class="btn-secondary">Application Form</a>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
        <a
          href="https://discord.gg/djmCF4DBaV"
          class="btn-text"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Discord
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@ywamsendai.org" class="btn-text">Email</a>
        <a
          href="https://ig.me/m/ywamsendai"
          class="btn-text"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Instagram
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>